---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Badge from '../components/Badge.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import StatBlock from '../components/StatBlock.astro';
import TestimonialBlock from '../components/TestimonialBlock.astro';
import SectionLabel from '../components/SectionLabel.astro';
import HourglassIcon from '../components/HourglassIcon.astro';
import ChessKnightIcon from '../components/ChessKnightIcon.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="The AI Revenue Ecosystem" activePage="home">

  <!-- SECTION 1: HERO -->
  <section class="relative bg-black pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-20 md:pb-16 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Radial glow behind headline -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      aria-hidden="true"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>

    <!-- Chess knight decorative (desktop only) -->
    <div class="absolute right-[5%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 hidden lg:block pointer-events-none text-white opacity-[0.06]" aria-hidden="true">
      <ChessKnightIcon size={200} />
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-0 relative z-10">
      <Badge variant="accent">The AI Revenue Ecosystem</Badge>

      <h1 class="text-[40px] md:text-[56px] lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-none tracking-tighter text-white mt-4 max-w-[800px]">
        AI Is Not a Technology Project.<br />
        It's a Revenue Strategy.
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-normal leading-relaxed text-neutral-400 mt-6 max-w-[600px]">
        Reis IA builds AI systems that generate revenue, trains agencies to sell AI solutions, and creates the partnerships that scale it all — through one connected ecosystem.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 mt-10">
        <Button variant="hero" href="#booking">
          Book a Free AI Revenue Assessment &#8594;
        </Button>
        <Button variant="secondary" href="#pillars">
          See How It Works &#8594;
        </Button>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-3">No pitch. No fluff. 30 minutes, a clear map of where AI makes money in your business.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: MANIFESTO -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 py-24 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-0">
      <div class="max-w-[720px]">
        <SectionLabel>What We Believe</SectionLabel>

        <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[42px] font-semibold text-white leading-tight mt-6" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
          We believe most companies are failing with AI — not because the technology doesn't work, but because they're asking the wrong question.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-[17px] text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Everyone is building AI.</p>
          <p>Chatbots. Automations. Agents. Dashboards.</p>
          <p>Most of it looks impressive in a demo and collects dust in production.</p>
          <p>The reason is simple: they started with the technology and hoped for business results.</p>
          <p>We start differently.</p>
          <p>We start with one question: <strong class="text-white font-semibold">Where is the revenue?</strong></p>
          <p>That question changes everything. It changes what gets built, what gets measured, and what actually makes a difference in your business.</p>

          <!-- Chess motif variation (ADDED 2026-03-11) -->
          <p>Winning with AI is not about moving first. It's about moving right.</p>
          <p>A chess player doesn't place pieces randomly and hope for checkmate. Every position is deliberate. Every move follows a strategy defined before the game begins.</p>
          <p>That's the Revenue-First approach. We map the board — your business, your revenue gaps, your highest-leverage opportunities — before a single system is built. Then we build with precision.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-white font-semibold">The difference between a tool and a weapon is the strategy behind it.</strong></p>

          <p>We call this the Revenue-First approach. It's the foundation of everything Reis IA does — whether we're implementing AI systems for your company, mentoring agencies to sell AI services, or building the partnerships that scale it all.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white leading-snug">
            AI for the sake of AI is a science experiment.<br />
            AI for revenue is a business strategy.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[17px] text-neutral-400 mt-2">That's the only kind we build.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: ECOSYSTEM PILLARS -->
  <section id="pillars" class="bg-black py-24 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-0">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <SectionLabel>The Ecosystem</SectionLabel>
        <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[42px] font-semibold text-white mt-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
          One relationship. Four ways to win with AI.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <!-- Builder Card -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors duration-200 flex flex-col reveal-up">
          <ChessKnightIcon size={40} class="text-accent mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Position Your Agency Ahead of the Market</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-neutral-400 mb-6 flex-1">
            The agencies winning with AI are not the most technical. They're the best positioned. Builder teaches you to map the revenue opportunity before touching the technology — so every move your agency makes is intentional, not reactive.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" aria-label="Builder features">
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>A sellable AI offer, built during the program</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Client acquisition systems that work</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Direct access to Moroni and the Reis IA methodology</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Your first project delivered — with support</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[13px] font-medium text-neutral-500 mb-6">While most agencies react to AI, Builder clients are already playing the next move.</p>
          <a href="/builder" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Apply to Builder &#8594;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Systems Card -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors duration-200 flex flex-col reveal-up reveal-delay-1">
          <HourglassIcon size={40} class="text-accent mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Deploy AI That Generates Revenue</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-neutral-400 mb-6 flex-1">
            Done-for-you AI implementation for companies ready to move from "AI strategy" to "AI results." We build the systems, integrate them, and make sure they produce measurable outcomes.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" aria-label="Systems features">
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>AI sales agents that qualify and follow up</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>AI support systems that convert, not just answer</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Operational automations that free your team for growth</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Full CRM, WhatsApp, and API integrations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[13px] font-medium text-neutral-500 mb-6">Fixed pricing. 60-day performance guarantee. And the one thing most vendors can't give you back: time. AI doesn't just cut costs — it returns hours. Hours that compound into revenue.</p>
          <a href="/systems" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Book an AI Revenue Audit &#8594;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Partners Card -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors duration-200 flex flex-col reveal-up reveal-delay-2">
          <ChessKnightIcon size={40} class="text-accent mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Add AI Revenue Without Adding Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-neutral-400 mb-6 flex-1">
            The smartest move in business is building capability without carrying all the cost. Reis IA Partners gives your agency the AI implementation backbone — so you sell high-ticket projects with confidence while we handle the technical execution. You keep the client relationship. We deliver the result.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" aria-label="Partners features">
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>An experienced technical partner behind every project you sell</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Revenue you couldn't have earned without hiring engineers</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>A model that scales: more partners, more projects, more margin</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[13px] font-medium text-neutral-500 mb-6">The agencies scaling fastest aren't building AI teams. They're building AI partnerships.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Learn About Partners &#8594;</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Network Card -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-colors duration-200 flex flex-col reveal-up reveal-delay-3">
          <svg class="h-10 w-auto text-accent mb-6" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="20" cy="8" r="4" />
            <circle cx="8" cy="30" r="4" />
            <circle cx="32" cy="30" r="4" />
            <line x1="20" y1="12" x2="8" y2="26" />
            <line x1="20" y1="12" x2="32" y2="26" />
            <line x1="12" y1="30" x2="28" y2="30" />
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">The AI Revenue Community</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-neutral-400 mb-6 flex-1">
            Events, education, collaboration, and a network of practitioners who are actually doing it. Not just learning — building.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" aria-label="Network features">
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Live events and workshops</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Specialist community access</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Ongoing AI education and case studies</li>
            <li class="text-sm text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent" aria-hidden="true">—</span>Strategic collaborations</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Join the Network &#8594;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: INTERACTIVE DEMO -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 py-24 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-0">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <SectionLabel>See It Working</SectionLabel>
        <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[42px] font-semibold text-white mt-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
          This is what Revenue-First AI looks like in production.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-400 mt-4 max-w-[600px] mx-auto">
          Not mockups. Not demos. Real systems deployed in real businesses.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Demo card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-neutral-950 relative placeholder-content flex items-end justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <polygon points="18,12 36,24 18,36" fill="white" opacity="0.4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-600 text-center px-4 pb-3 relative z-10">[PLACEHOLDER: 90-second screen recording — AI Lead Qualification Agent]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">An AI that qualifies leads before your sales team touches them</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">See a live AI agent handling inbound leads across WhatsApp and web — asking the right questions, scoring each lead, and routing only the qualified ones to a human.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Demo card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-neutral-950 relative placeholder-content flex items-end justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <polygon points="18,12 36,24 18,36" fill="white" opacity="0.4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-600 text-center px-4 pb-3 relative z-10">[PLACEHOLDER: 90-second screen recording — AI Customer Support Agent]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">A support agent that resolves 70% of tickets before a human reads them</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Watch an AI handle common support queries, escalate edge cases intelligently, and feed everything back into a CRM — automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Demo card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-neutral-950 relative placeholder-content flex items-end justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <polygon points="18,12 36,24 18,36" fill="white" opacity="0.4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-600 text-center px-4 pb-3 relative z-10">[PLACEHOLDER: 90-second screen recording — AI Proposal Generator]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">From client brief to AI project proposal in under 10 minutes</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Built for Builder clients — a tool that takes a client's business context and produces a structured AI service proposal with pricing, scope, and ROI projections.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 mb-6">Want to see this built for your business?</p>
        <Button variant="hero" href="#booking">Book a Free AI Revenue Assessment &#8594;</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5: RESULTS / SOCIAL PROOF -->
  <section class="bg-black py-24 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-0">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <SectionLabel>Results</SectionLabel>
        <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[42px] font-semibold text-white mt-4 max-w-[800px] mx-auto leading-tight" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
          <span class="inline-flex items-baseline gap-2">
            <HourglassIcon size={24} class="text-white opacity-40 inline-block align-middle" />
            Every month in the Prototype Graveyard is a month that doesn't come back.
          </span>
          <br />Here's what it looks like when companies escape it.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Market data stats with chess grid texture -->
      <div class="relative py-8">
        <div class="chess-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-100" style="mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 40%, transparent 80%); -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 40%, transparent 80%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative z-10">
          <StatBlock value="91%" label="of SMBs using AI report revenue increases" />
          <StatBlock value="74%" label="achieve ROI within year one" />
          <StatBlock value="67%" label="success rate for specialist vendors" />
          <StatBlock value="22%" label="success rate for generalists" muted={true} />
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-[17px] text-neutral-400 text-center max-w-[720px] mx-auto mt-8 mb-16">
        The difference between those two numbers isn't technology. It's the time companies spend building the wrong thing first.
      </p>

      <!-- Case studies (placeholders) -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Case Study 1 -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 lg:p-12">
          <div class="placeholder-content rounded p-2 mb-6 inline-block">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-600">Placeholder — Case Study: Agency AI Revenue Stream</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:border-r lg:border-neutral-800 lg:pr-8">
              <p class="text-[48px] font-bold text-accent leading-none">[METRIC]</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">in new AI revenue</p>
              <p class="text-[48px] font-bold text-white leading-none mt-6">[METRIC]</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">new clients acquired</p>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">[Agency Name] — Digital Marketing Agency</p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-3">The situation:</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mt-2">Agency owner knew AI was coming but had no idea how to package or sell it. Losing clients to AI-enabled competitors.</p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-4">What we built:</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mt-2">[AI solution — structured AI offer + client acquisition system through Builder program]</p>
              <div class="mt-6">
                <TestimonialBlock
                  quote="[TESTIMONIAL — placeholder quote text]"
                  name="[Agency Owner Name]"
                  role="[Agency Name] — Digital Marketing Agency"
                  isPlaceholder={true}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Study 2 -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 lg:p-12">
          <div class="placeholder-content rounded p-2 mb-6 inline-block">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-600">Placeholder — Case Study: B2B Lead Qualification</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">[Company Name] — [Industry]</p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-3">The situation:</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mt-2">Sales team spending hours on unqualified leads. Pipeline full of noise. Revenue growth stalled.</p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-4">What we built:</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mt-2">AI lead qualification and routing system integrated with their CRM and WhatsApp.</p>
              <div class="mt-6">
                <TestimonialBlock
                  quote="[TESTIMONIAL — placeholder quote text]"
                  name="[Contact Name]"
                  role="[Company] — [Title]"
                  isPlaceholder={true}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:border-l lg:border-neutral-800 lg:pl-8">
              <p class="text-[48px] font-bold text-accent leading-none">[METRIC]%</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">increase in qualified leads</p>
              <p class="text-[48px] font-bold text-white leading-none mt-6">[METRIC]</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">hours/week returned to sales team</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Study 3 -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 lg:p-12">
          <div class="placeholder-content rounded p-2 mb-6 inline-block">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-600">Placeholder — Case Study: Support Automation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:border-r lg:border-neutral-800 lg:pr-8">
              <p class="text-[48px] font-bold text-accent leading-none">[METRIC]%</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">queries resolved automatically</p>
              <p class="text-[48px] font-bold text-white leading-none mt-6">[METRIC]</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">hours/week returned to founder</p>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
              <p class="text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">[Company Name] — [Industry]</p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-3">The situation:</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mt-2">Founder answering the same 40 questions daily. No capacity to grow.</p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-4">What we built:</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mt-2">AI support agent handling FAQs, booking, and escalation across WhatsApp and website.</p>
              <div class="mt-6">
                <TestimonialBlock
                  quote="[TESTIMONIAL — placeholder quote text]"
                  name="[Founder Name]"
                  role="[Company] — Founder"
                  isPlaceholder={true}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 6: FOUNDER STORY -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 py-24 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-0">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="w-full min-h-[300px] lg:min-h-[500px] bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center p-8 placeholder-content" loading="lazy">
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 text-center">[PLACEHOLDER: Professional photo of Moroni Reis. Dark/moody lighting. Desaturated. Gradient overlay from edges.]</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <SectionLabel>Why Reis IA Exists</SectionLabel>

          <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[42px] font-semibold text-white mt-4 leading-tight" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
            I spent years watching companies waste money on AI that never worked.
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-[17px] text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Moroni Reis is a digital marketing strategist and the founder of Reis IA, an AI Revenue Ecosystem that helps companies and digital agencies implement AI that generates measurable business results. With a decade of experience in marketing strategy, client acquisition, funnels, and launch systems, Moroni built Reis IA around a single insight: most AI projects fail because they start with the technology instead of the revenue opportunity.</p>
            <p>His Revenue-First Framework inverts that approach — mapping where AI creates the highest-leverage business impact before a single line of code is written. Through Reis IA's four-pillar ecosystem — Builder, Systems, Partners, and Network — he works with agencies wanting to sell AI, companies ready to deploy it, and entrepreneurs building new AI-powered business models.</p>
            <p>He operates at the intersection of the Brazilian and global markets, bringing a practical, no-fluff perspective to a space dominated by hype.</p>
            <p class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <HourglassIcon size={24} class="text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
